text: Elis Holmer (1 December 1893 - 29 February 1968) was a Swedish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1893 births Category:1968 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gothenburg
